HEADWORD: Primates
<hw>Pri*ma"tes</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The highest order of mammals. It includes man,
together with the apes and monkeys. Cf. <er>Pitheci</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
